parameters: How many more minutes do I have left?!
Can't he hear me with such big ears?
'Why are you so hard of hearing with such big ears?'
If I had a room like this, Dinah (the name of her pet cat)
would also be able to play freely…hm?
"This is a 'magical pill bottle'. If you fill it up with magic,
it'll turn into "medicine that shrinks your body".
…But what fun it would be to become tiny.
"It sounds fun, so why don't I just take it along with me?
"Perhaps I can play a trick on Mr. Rabbit!
"Now!...let's capture Mr. Rabbit hard of hearing,
and scream "Hello! Can you hear me?"
